Sample customized /etc/lightdm/lightdm.conf settings to allow an incoming
remote XDMCP client connection:

[SeatDefaults]
user-session=ubuntu
autologin-user=false
xserver-allow-tcp=true
greeter-session=unity-greeter

[XDMCPServer]
enabled=true
port=177


Reference:

http://jeffskinnerbox.me/posts/2014/Apr/29/howto-using-xephyr-to-create-a-new-display-in-a-window/
